# TypeScript

- Strict mode; no `any` without justified comment.
- Prefer `interface` for object shapes; `type` for unions.
- Async: always handle rejection; use Result patterns for expected failures.
- Import `@fieldforge/config` for brand colors — CSS vars `--brand-*`.
- Shared types from `packages/sdk` (OpenAPI-generated when available).

**React/Next.js:**
- Server Components default; `'use client'` only when needed.
- Colocate tests as `*.test.ts(x)` beside source.
- Mobile routes under `app/(mobile)/m/` use `usePlatform()` — never raw Capacitor in components.
